opinions.text:
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperisdenied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fourth Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
Justice KAGANtook no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
